                  </cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                     <quote>frenare</quote>
                  </cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                     <quote>refrenare</quote>
                  </cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                     <quote>coërcere</quote>
                  </cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ንኅንቃ፡ ለነፍስነ፡ ወንልጕማ፡ ከመ፡ ፈረስ፡ ኀያል፡ ወድሩክ፡</foreign>
